PROCEDURE BuildCustList :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     Builds the temp table of customers   
  Parameters:  Company Code, Customer list logical and/or customer range
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
DEFINE INPUT PARAMETER ipcCompany AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
